n=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/urakasan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rakasan</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Apprentice</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/14/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>7:34:15 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Harvest bugged?</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Am I the one who is bugged here or is the spell? The spell icon for harvest will refresh alot sooner then you can actually use the spell. Thus you don't know when the spell is ready for the next cast. Is this a bug, a verant way of making it harder, or me? I've reported this on several occasions but no news yet. I hope it is resolved soon.<br>
<br>
</font><P><i><font face="Lucida Calligraphy"><font color=red><font size=+5>R</font></font><font color=red>akasan</font> <font size=+5><font color=red>T</font></font><font color=red>shar</font></font></i><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/urusttika.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rusttika</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Apprentice</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/14/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>9:15:13 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Harvest bugged?</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Well I can Confirm the problem. I have it happen to me Mainly after I take a drink of sow potion it pops back up afterward.<br>
Its not just you.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#33333><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=sarxos>sarxos</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Apprentice</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/14/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>11:44:59 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Harvest bugged?</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Yes, in most cases i have to press the icon 7 times to get it to fire (normally 7, 3 or none strangely enough) and in that time i am not sitting medding. Irritating bug, not fatal, but has been there for a few weeks now.<br>
<br>
Sarxos<br>
  - 60 Sorcerer, Innoruuk</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=quiksilver1>Quiksilver1</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Wizard</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/14/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>8:01:23 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Yes it is bugged</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I've had to unmemorize and then wait 10 minutes more before I could recast, usually I have to click 3 times straight then it will cast, or sometimes more.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#33333><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ucaladdortalonthael.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Caladdor Talonthael</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Wizard</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/16/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>7:32:47 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://www.westerndecadence.org/photos/calthumb.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Harvest bugged?</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">The only problem I've had with Harvest is that if I stand up from medding, I've got to move a step or two one way or the other to get it to cast. Otherwise it just won't cast.<br>
<br>
The only spell I've found so far with that problem.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uhippastus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippastus</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Apprentice</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/20/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>6:16:54 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Harvest bugged?</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">It happens all the time.  It's realy simple really, and related to a beneficial bug.  Any time you activate a magical item (like a sow potion, staff of temp flux, jboots, etc) or your weapon procs, all your spell gems pop up.  This can be used to nuke slightly quicker, but can be very annoying in the case of harvest because the gem is up long before you can use it.  See, both the client and server maintain timers for spells.  In cases like nukes where the refresh time is relatively small the cient doesn't have time to confirmn that you can actualy cast it with the server.  But with Harvest and it's 10 minute cast time the client asks the server if it's ok to cast the spell each time.  Thus you have your gem up but when you hit it nothing happens.<br>
<br>
-Hippastus Pythagoris &lt;Clan Destine&gt;<br>
52 Wizard, Terris-Thule</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#33333><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/useverinewolfe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Severine Wolfe</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Wizard</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/22/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>12:03:40 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://www.clan-donald.com/screenshots/severine.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Harvest bugged?</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Actually, on Solusek Ro I have noticed that if I am standing right next to a wall the spell will not fire off... If I take a couple steps away it fires... No Problem.<br>
<br>
